Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:55.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCB3B17&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}So tenderly and endlessly\N如此温柔又无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCB3B17&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}You made me whole, you made me whole\N你完整了我的世界
